## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the full complexity of religious evolution. Additionally, the historical record is incomplete, particularly for prehistoric religions, leading to reliance on archaeological interpretations that are subject to change with new discoveries. Furthermore, the dynamic nature of religion means that ongoing changes may not be fully captured in this report.